### Additional Comments:

This is a battery-powered temperature sensor designed for home automation applications. The device requires a Zigbee gateway to function.

Based on the device interview, it supports:
- Temperature measurement (cluster 1026) - currently reading 21.9C
- Battery monitoring (cluster 1) - showing 21V battery voltage and 100% remaining
- Basic Zigbee functionality (clusters 0, 3)
- OTA updates (cluster 25)
- Time synchronization (cluster 10)

