### Additional Comments:

This is a soil moisture and temperature sensor designed for garden automation and irrigation monitoring. The device is battery-powered (2x AAA batteries, not included) and requires a Zigbee gateway to function. 

Based on the device interview, it supports:
- Temperature measurement (cluster 1026)
- Relative humidity measurement (cluster 1029) 
- Battery monitoring (cluster 1)
- Basic Zigbee functionality (clusters 0, 3)

The device is purchased from AliExpress and appears to be similar to other soil humidity sensors already supported in the app but with a different manufacturer ID (_TZE200_wqashyqo).

Purchase link: https://www.aliexpress.com/item/1005008919122614.html?spm=a2g0o.order_list.order_list_main.11.a64f18025qi6ll#nav-specification

